cs.CL, cs.SI, cs.IR, cs.CY, cs.SD

This paper is likely to belong to the Computational Linguistics (cs.CL) sub-category as it proposes a machine learning classifier based on linguistic analysis to detect clickbait posts in online social media. It also uses image-related features, which could place it in the Social and Information Networks (cs.SI) sub-category. Information Retrieval (cs.IR) could also be a likely sub-category as the paper deals with detecting relevant information in social media posts. Cybersecurity (cs.CY) and Software Engineering (cs.SD) could also be possible sub-categories as the paper deals with detecting abusive content and developing a machine learning classifier, respectively.
